      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure is straightforward, involving basic SQL operations such as variable declaration, simple SELECT queries, conditional logic with an IF statement, and an UPDATE operation. It does not involve complex joins, subqueries, or intricate logic, making it relatively easy to understand and maintain."
        }
      ]
    },
